    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个图来展示cherry-pick的典型场景：从main分支挑一个提交到develop分支。整体布局用从左到右的方向，标题就叫\"Cherry-pick from main (left-to-right)\"吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "gitGraph LR",
        "main",
        "develop",
        "cherry-pick"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，我先确认一下结构：先有一个初始commit，然后分出develop分支，develop上再做一个commit。之后切回main做标记为\"A\"的commit，再切回develop做commit，最后把main上的\"A\" cherry-pick过来。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit",
        "branch develop",
        "checkout main",
        "commit id:\"A\"",
        "checkout develop",
        "cherry-pick id:\"A\""
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，就是这个流程。关键是那个id为\"A\"的commit要在main上，然后被cherry-pick到develop分支，这样能清晰展示跨分支取提交的场景。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit id:\"A\"",
        "main",
        "develop",
        "cherry-pick id:\"A\""
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把框架搭好了：标题设置完成，方向设为LR，main分支先有初始commit，然后branch develop并commit，checkout回main后做了标记为\"A\"的commit。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "gitGraph LR",
        "commit",
        "branch develop",
        "checkout main",
        "commit id:\"A\""
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "develop分支上在cherry-pick之前再加一个commit吧，这样develop就有两个自己的提交，然后再cherry-pick main的\"A\"过来，历史线会更真实一些。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "commit",
        "cherry-pick"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：checkout develop之后加了一个commit，然后用cherry-pick id:\"A\"把main上的那个提交挑过来了。现在develop分支上有三个提交了——两个自己的加上cherry-pick来的\"A\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout develop",
        "commit",
        "cherry-pick id:\"A\"",
        "develop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美，这个图很清楚地展示了cherry-pick的核心机制：不合并整个分支，只挑选特定的commit。从左到右的布局也让时间线很直观。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "gitGraph LR",
        "cherry-pick id:\"A\"",
